<h1 class = "javascript-title"> Bottle</h1>
<p>Bottle is a fast, simple and lightweight WSGI micro web-framework for Python. It is distributed as a single file module and has no dependencies other than the Python Standard Library.</p>
<ul>
    <li> Routing: Requests to function-call mapping with support for clean and dynamic URLs.</li>
    <li> Templates: Fast and pythonic built-in template engine and support for mako, jinja2 and cheetah templates.  </li>
    <li> Utilities: Convenient access to form data, file uploads, cookies, headers and other HTTP-related metadata.</li>
    <li> Server: Built-in HTTP development server and support for paste, bjoern, gae, cherrypy or any other WSGI capable HTTP server.</li>
</ul>  
